text: Afsar () is a 2018 Indian film in Punjabi language directed by Gulshan Singh, with actors such as Tarsem Jassar, Nimrat Khaira, Gurpreet Ghuggi and Karamjit Anmol playing. It was released on 5 October 2018 and the film received good reviews from the public but mixed reviews from critics. == References == Category:2010s Indian movies
